{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/i-have-a-profile-picture/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Coding Armadillo's Blog","author":"Coding Armadillo"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3dc9b479-63e1-5a53-906e-755e48311aac","excerpt":"After saying “Hello World” I struggled to make myself a pretty profile picture.\nBeing no designer I tried to use an online tool to visualize my idea.\nAnd it…","html":"<p>After saying “Hello World” I struggled to make myself a pretty profile picture.\nBeing no designer I tried to use an <a href=\"https://www.freelogodesign.org/\">online tool</a> to visualize my idea.\nAnd it came out like the following. :(</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 214px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bb8956a1d35f9d1c5a413f948d0fce6a/a48b3/Coding-Armadillo-concept.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.75675675675676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"concept\"\n        title=\"concept\"\n        src=\"/static/bb8956a1d35f9d1c5a413f948d0fce6a/a48b3/Coding-Armadillo-concept.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bb8956a1d35f9d1c5a413f948d0fce6a/12f09/Coding-Armadillo-concept.png 148w,\n/static/bb8956a1d35f9d1c5a413f948d0fce6a/a48b3/Coding-Armadillo-concept.png 214w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 214px) 100vw, 214px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Luckily I stumbled across <a href=\"https://emcallahan.com/\">Emily</a>’s <a href=\"https://dribbble.com/emily-callahan\">dribbble</a> profile and loved her illustrative version of armadillo at first sight.\nWe got in touch and she agreed to make me a profile picture.\nWe started with a sketch.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f9a8bdfa96a6bc7b37c23aec551893db/a2510/Coding-Armadillo-sketch1-emcallahan-wm.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sketch1\"\n        title=\"sketch1\"\n        src=\"/static/f9a8bdfa96a6bc7b37c23aec551893db/1c72d/Coding-Armadillo-sketch1-emcallahan-wm.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f9a8bdfa96a6bc7b37c23aec551893db/a80bd/Coding-Armadillo-sketch1-emcallahan-wm.jpg 148w,\n/static/f9a8bdfa96a6bc7b37c23aec551893db/1c91a/Coding-Armadillo-sketch1-emcallahan-wm.jpg 295w,\n/static/f9a8bdfa96a6bc7b37c23aec551893db/1c72d/Coding-Armadillo-sketch1-emcallahan-wm.jpg 590w,\n/static/f9a8bdfa96a6bc7b37c23aec551893db/a8a14/Coding-Armadillo-sketch1-emcallahan-wm.jpg 885w,\n/static/f9a8bdfa96a6bc7b37c23aec551893db/a2510/Coding-Armadillo-sketch1-emcallahan-wm.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>We exchanged ideas and got a new sketch.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5f330e7bd6dffcc495de730de283d85b/a2510/Coding-Armadillo-sketch2-emcallahan-wm.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sketch2\"\n        title=\"sketch2\"\n        src=\"/static/5f330e7bd6dffcc495de730de283d85b/1c72d/Coding-Armadillo-sketch2-emcallahan-wm.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5f330e7bd6dffcc495de730de283d85b/a80bd/Coding-Armadillo-sketch2-emcallahan-wm.jpg 148w,\n/static/5f330e7bd6dffcc495de730de283d85b/1c91a/Coding-Armadillo-sketch2-emcallahan-wm.jpg 295w,\n/static/5f330e7bd6dffcc495de730de283d85b/1c72d/Coding-Armadillo-sketch2-emcallahan-wm.jpg 590w,\n/static/5f330e7bd6dffcc495de730de283d85b/a8a14/Coding-Armadillo-sketch2-emcallahan-wm.jpg 885w,\n/static/5f330e7bd6dffcc495de730de283d85b/a2510/Coding-Armadillo-sketch2-emcallahan-wm.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Then lovely colors were added!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d839eee572fff12648e1bc6ae6df3783/a2510/Coding-Armadillo-color-rough-emcallahan--wm.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"color-rough\"\n        title=\"color-rough\"\n        src=\"/static/d839eee572fff12648e1bc6ae6df3783/1c72d/Coding-Armadillo-color-rough-emcallahan--wm.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d839eee572fff12648e1bc6ae6df3783/a80bd/Coding-Armadillo-color-rough-emcallahan--wm.jpg 148w,\n/static/d839eee572fff12648e1bc6ae6df3783/1c91a/Coding-Armadillo-color-rough-emcallahan--wm.jpg 295w,\n/static/d839eee572fff12648e1bc6ae6df3783/1c72d/Coding-Armadillo-color-rough-emcallahan--wm.jpg 590w,\n/static/d839eee572fff12648e1bc6ae6df3783/a8a14/Coding-Armadillo-color-rough-emcallahan--wm.jpg 885w,\n/static/d839eee572fff12648e1bc6ae6df3783/a2510/Coding-Armadillo-color-rough-emcallahan--wm.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Finally I have an awesome profile picture!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/07d30e5dd989f45cbe1a4060779eae93/a2510/Coding-Armadillo-final-emcallahan-wm.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"final\"\n        title=\"final\"\n        src=\"/static/07d30e5dd989f45cbe1a4060779eae93/1c72d/Coding-Armadillo-final-emcallahan-wm.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/07d30e5dd989f45cbe1a4060779eae93/a80bd/Coding-Armadillo-final-emcallahan-wm.jpg 148w,\n/static/07d30e5dd989f45cbe1a4060779eae93/1c91a/Coding-Armadillo-final-emcallahan-wm.jpg 295w,\n/static/07d30e5dd989f45cbe1a4060779eae93/1c72d/Coding-Armadillo-final-emcallahan-wm.jpg 590w,\n/static/07d30e5dd989f45cbe1a4060779eae93/a8a14/Coding-Armadillo-final-emcallahan-wm.jpg 885w,\n/static/07d30e5dd989f45cbe1a4060779eae93/a2510/Coding-Armadillo-final-emcallahan-wm.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>If you need some artwork done, please <a href=\"https://emcallahan.com/contact\">contact</a> Emily. She’s amazing!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"I Have A Profile Picture!","date":"October 09, 2019","description":"Evolution of the Coding Armadillo's profile picture"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/i-have-a-profile-picture/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/hello-world/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Hello World"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["1589750121","63159454"]}